  <brief_title>Elective Neurectomy During Inguinal Hernia Repair</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Elective Intraoperative Neurectomy on Chronic Pain After Lichtenstein Hernia Repair. A Prospective, Single-blind, Randomized, Controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
